<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<p>
When I'm invisible, even with an artifact and a ring plus the potion, the lowliest of the low archers (who can't see me) hit me with 100% accuracy. Same for mages. 
</p>
<p>
This derives from the "archers and bolts aimed at player always hit" implementation, which doesn't check for succesful invisibility. 
</p>
